<p begin="0t" end="22510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">Processed by 繁化姬 dict-de8716aa-r1017 @ 2023/01/29 23:05:25 | https://zhconvert.org</p>
<p begin="22510000t" end="43360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">我知道真凶是谁</p>
<p begin="56290000t" end="80900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">虽然不是什么需要着急的问题</p>
<p begin="80900000t" end="114280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">不过我就顺便说说这部分该怎么解决吧</p>
<p begin="356590000t" end="379960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">在四季中转瞬即逝之冬</p>
<p begin="379960000t" end="408320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">有位如雪般的美人</p>
<p begin="408320000t" end="430840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">折羽织缎只为祈愿</p>
<p begin="430840000t" end="459200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">落下泪珠化身为鹤</p>
<p begin="459200000t" end="481730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">踏上寻找世界尽头旅途</p>
<p begin="481730000t" end="510090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">沙漠中的少年</p>
<p begin="510090000t" end="532610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">释放了神灯的精灵</p>
<p begin="532610000t" end="560970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">获得无可取代的财富</p>
<p begin="560970000t" end="613100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">精巧隐瞒的真象 形同幻化</p>
<p begin="613100000t" end="647300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">之中能有什么意义?</p>
<p begin="647300000t" end="686920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">人生! 一切! 皆是! 神秘!</p>
<p begin="702360000t" end="746560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">让我们背对太阳</p>
<p begin="746560000t" end="800370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">轻轻为无形的未来染上色彩</p>
<p begin="800370000t" end="848760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">来杯刚泡好热腾腾的红茶吧</p>
<p begin="848760000t" end="877540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">宴会已经开始了</p>
<p begin="877540000t" end="911740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">快告诉我 夜色中的故事</p>
<p begin="1092330000t" end="1114020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">你说你知道真凶是谁</p>
<p begin="1114020000t" end="1128610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">这是什么意思</p>
<p begin="1134030000t" end="1159060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">没错  简单来说</p>
<p begin="1159060000t" end="1197430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">室井先生你已经脱离险境了</p>
<p begin="1197430000t" end="1215780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">就算我不出手</p>
<p begin="1215780000t" end="1239150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">被逮捕的可能性也很低</p>
<p begin="1277510000t" end="1322150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">但  但是警察有在监视我吧</p>
<p begin="1322150000t" end="1342170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">那是你的被害妄想</p>
<p begin="1342170000t" end="1383460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">警察也没闲到能分人手去管嫌疑很轻的人</p>
<p begin="1383460000t" end="1414310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">那为什么我的嫌疑突然变轻了</p>
<p begin="1419320000t" end="1445610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">从被害者美春小姐的遗体来看</p>
<p begin="1445610000t" end="1463540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">财物  钥匙</p>
<p begin="1463540000t" end="1492310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">以及身份证件跟手机等都原封不动</p>
<p begin="1497740000t" end="1514010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">衣服十分整齐</p>
<p begin="1514010000t" end="1544440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">住家也没有遭入侵的痕迹</p>
<p begin="1551550000t" end="1563220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">这就是原因了</p>
<p begin="1569060000t" end="1604920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">美春小姐很可能是被犯人带去…</p>
<p begin="1604920000t" end="1629120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">或是被约在杀人现场见面的</p>
<p begin="1635800000t" end="1651220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">那么想必她跟犯人</p>
<p begin="1651220000t" end="1679590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">会有段碰面并交谈的时间</p>
<p begin="1685010000t" end="1697110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">这么一来</p>
<p begin="1697110000t" end="1712950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">如果犯人是室井先生的话</p>
<p begin="1712950000t" end="1722960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">美春小姐应该会说</p>
<p begin="1729210000t" end="1758830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">"我要是被杀的话  你一定会被抓"</p>
<p begin="1758830000t" end="1834730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">"我已经写了信留给警察 说自己遭遇不测的话就是你下的手"</p>
<p begin="1847250000t" end="1863520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">"只要你乖乖离开"</p>
<p begin="1863520000t" end="1881450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">"我就不会把今天的事说出去"</p>
<p begin="1881450000t" end="1909810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">她应该会试着这样跟你交涉吧</p>
<p begin="1917330000t" end="1957770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">告发信虽然是在死后报复犯人的武器</p>
<p begin="1957770000t" end="1996160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">但在那之前会先成为 保护自己免于一死的盾牌</p>
<p begin="2001160000t" end="2035360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">美春小姐若是有被你杀害的危机感</p>
<p begin="2035360000t" end="2079150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">想必会利用告发信来保身</p>
<p begin="2085820000t" end="2104180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">毕竟根据交涉结果</p>
<p begin="2104180000t" end="2129610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">她很有可能逃过一死</p>
<p begin="2136700000t" end="2165910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">所以她不可能不把这招拿出来用</p>
<p begin="2180080000t" end="2191760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">如果听了这些话之后</p>
<p begin="2191760000t" end="2218040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">你还是杀死美春小姐的话…</p>
<p begin="2218040000t" end="2250150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">就算告发信可能是她捏造的</p>
<p begin="2250150000t" end="2289370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">也应该会考虑该怎么处理</p>
<p begin="2289370000t" end="2298950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">没错</p>
<p begin="2317720000t" end="2327740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">若是如此</p>
<p begin="2327740000t" end="2351930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">你首先应该会思考能不能拿回告发信</p>
<p begin="2351930000t" end="2382780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">打算去她的住处翻找</p>
<p begin="2388200000t" end="2398220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">但是</p>
<p begin="2398220000t" end="2448260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">这么做可能会被公寓或附近的监视器拍到</p>
<p begin="2448260000t" end="2474130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">如果她藏在住处之外的地方</p>
<p begin="2474130000t" end="2509170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">更会因为多余的行动暴露自己行踪</p>
<p begin="2521680000t" end="2543780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">或许就会因此放弃拿回告发信</p>
<p begin="2549620000t" end="2562130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">既然这样</p>
<p begin="2562130000t" end="2590070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">则可能转向为了让犯案动机不局限于仇恨</p>
<p begin="2590070000t" end="2630530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">带走被害者身上的财物装成抢劫</p>
<p begin="2637620000t" end="2670160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">或是做些看起来像是性犯罪的手脚</p>
<p begin="2676840000t" end="2714780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">其他至少也会想办法把尸体藏起来</p>
<p begin="2714780000t" end="2737300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">为了让人无法第一时间确认身份</p>
<p begin="2737300000t" end="2756920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">也可能会破坏指纹跟牙齿</p>
<p begin="2756920000t" end="2781100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">或是带走证件和手机</p>
<p begin="2786940000t" end="2815720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">做出这种干扰搜查的行动吧</p>
<p begin="2815720000t" end="2843240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">但实际上  完全没有这些痕迹</p>
<p begin="2843240000t" end="2884950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">警方很快就认定犯案的动机是仇恨</p>
<p begin="2895380000t" end="2928340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">然后警察向你问话时</p>
<p begin="2928340000t" end="2960450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">问你不在场证明  无法立刻回答</p>
<p begin="2960450000t" end="3007570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">跟很像美春小姐的人一起被监视器拍到</p>
<p begin="3007570000t" end="3035930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">要求说明时也回答得很敷衍</p>
<p begin="3043030000t" end="3058460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">这不就太奇怪了吗</p>
<p begin="3073070000t" end="3107670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">你如果知道美春小姐那封告发信的存在</p>
<p begin="3107670000t" end="3141050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">自然能想到自己迟早会被警方调查</p>
<p begin="3141050000t" end="3155640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">不太可能什么准备都不做</p>
<p begin="3155640000t" end="3188600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">尽说些加深自己嫌疑的话</p>
<p begin="3209440000t" end="3232380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">警方也注意到这个矛盾点</p>
<p begin="3232380000t" end="3274100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">现在正致力寻找其他有犯案动机的人</p>
<p begin="3274100000t" end="3301200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">如果你没和雪女扯上关系</p>
<p begin="3301200000t" end="3325810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">就不会留下监视器的影像</p>
<p begin="3325810000t" end="3364610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">也会明确回答自己没有不在场证明吧</p>
<p begin="3364610000t" end="3389630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">没有不在场证明就无法查验真伪</p>
<p begin="3389630000t" end="3425070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">你从不跟邻居往来  也问不出什么线索</p>
<p begin="3433000000t" end="3458020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">调查将变得更困难</p>
<p begin="3458020000t" end="3482210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">反而会加深你的嫌疑吧</p>
<p begin="3502660000t" end="3536440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">雪女似乎认为自己害你陷入险境</p>
<p begin="3536440000t" end="3558550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">显得很沮丧</p>
<p begin="3558550000t" end="3580240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">事实上正好相反</p>
<p begin="3580240000t" end="3598170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">这么说来很讽刺</p>
<p begin="3598170000t" end="3616510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">不过你因为不能明讲雪女存在</p>
<p begin="3616510000t" end="3635710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">才做出的可疑行径</p>
<p begin="3635710000t" end="3655310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">反而让你躲过这次的危机</p>
<p begin="3674080000t" end="3727040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">那美春掌心的文字又是怎么回事</p>
<p begin="3733720000t" end="3762500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">那的确像是要写我的名字</p>
<p begin="3772500000t" end="3785860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">美春小姐应该是</p>
<p begin="3785860000t" end="3831320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">在明确知道犯人身份的状况下被杀死的</p>
<p begin="3831320000t" end="3862180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">然后  既然你不是犯人</p>
<p begin="3862180000t" end="3898460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">应该可以推测是真凶为了嫁祸给你</p>
<p begin="3898460000t" end="3946850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">才在杀死她之后写上去的</p>
<p begin="3957690000t" end="3976050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">这是很常见的手法</p>
<p begin="3976050000t" end="3995640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">不  可是…</p>
<p begin="3995640000t" end="4025260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">我在表面上并没有杀害美春的动机</p>
<p begin="4038600000t" end="4084080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">知道我是差点被美春杀才离婚的话还好说</p>
<p begin="4084080000t" end="4108670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">但这件事我没告诉过任何人</p>
<p begin="4108670000t" end="4150810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">她也不会把自己杀人未遂的事告诉别人吧</p>
<p begin="4150810000t" end="4190430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">有谁会想要这样陷害我?</p>
<p begin="4195430000t" end="4234630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">这世上也有人会因为外遇杀人</p>
<p begin="4234630000t" end="4254250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">可能是出于扭曲的独占欲</p>
<p begin="4254250000t" end="4274680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">或是觉得被伤害了自尊</p>
<p begin="4280930000t" end="4302620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">要是我男友劈腿</p>
<p begin="4302620000t" end="4322230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">我也会想杀了他</p>
<p begin="4328890000t" end="4343070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">这样啊</p>
<p begin="4343070000t" end="4374780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">我一直觉得美春外遇我也有错</p>
<p begin="4383960000t" end="4417320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">-公主殿下的恋人不是杀不死的吗…<br />-所以从没往那方面想过</p>
<p begin="4422740000t" end="4447350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">只要和过去背叛你的朋友</p>
<p begin="4447350000t" end="4478630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">在几年后死掉的事实连接起来</p>
<p begin="4478630000t" end="4505740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">你就会给人无法原谅别人背叛</p>
<p begin="4505740000t" end="4531610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">个性固执的印象</p>
<p begin="4531610000t" end="4552880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">说不定你以前公司的同伴</p>
<p begin="4552880000t" end="4574560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">也暗中害怕你会报复</p>
<p begin="4574560000t" end="4612090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">进而在你不知道的地方谣传这些印象</p>
<p begin="4618770000t" end="4654230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">所以犯人才在杀害美春小姐之后</p>
<p begin="4654230000t" end="4678000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">写下一部分你的名字</p>
<p begin="4678000000t" end="4699270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">以增加你的嫌疑</p>
<p begin="4713450000t" end="4750980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">然后为了让警方认为你是犯人</p>
<p begin="4750980000t" end="4789780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">事件发生时  你还不能有不在场证明</p>
<p begin="4813960000t" end="4854010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">-所以犯人会刻意安排…<br />-我能感觉到…</p>
<p begin="4854010000t" end="4889460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">-或事先确认没有人能替你作证<br />-越来越接近真相了</p>
<p begin="4896970000t" end="4915310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">-并且能够做到这件事<br />-我是不是</p>
<p begin="4915310000t" end="4942850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">-或是说实际做了的人就是真凶<br />-不该再让她说下去了</p>
<p begin="4942850000t" end="4955360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">室井先生</p>
<p begin="4955360000t" end="4969950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">依你看来</p>
<p begin="4969950000t" end="4995400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">能做到这点的人应该很有限吧</p>
<p begin="4995400000t" end="5015410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">有这可能性的人…</p>
<p begin="5024180000t" end="5037930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">只有一个</p>
<p begin="5063380000t" end="5090070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">难道说…是饭冢?</p>
<p begin="5097590000t" end="5106340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">没错</p>
<p begin="5117610000t" end="5135530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">饭冢渚</p>
<p begin="5135530000t" end="5153470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">她就是犯人</p>
<p begin="5316550000t" end="5359930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">(雪女的纯真)</p>
<p begin="5464610000t" end="5477970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">昌幸</p>
<p begin="5503410000t" end="5530520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">我也曾经跟你说过一些</p>
<p begin="5530520000t" end="5560540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">饭冢是公司被并购时</p>
<p begin="5560540000t" end="5601420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">少数站在我这边的员工之一</p>
<p begin="5601420000t" end="5638950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">她接手我离开公司前正在筹备的工作</p>
<p begin="5638950000t" end="5655650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">是个非常能干的部下</p>
<p begin="5667310000t" end="5687340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">也是我被赶出公司后</p>
<p begin="5687340000t" end="5709860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">唯一愿意跟我保持联络的人</p>
<p begin="5715280000t" end="5739050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">我本来以为她只是注重客套</p>
<p begin="5739050000t" end="5764080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">没想到她竟然对我怀恨在心</p>
<p begin="5776180000t" end="5799530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">那天晚上七点左右</p>
<p begin="5799530000t" end="5831240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">因为雪女来我家  所以我做了天妇罗</p>
<p begin="5831240000t" end="5847920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">她就是那时打电话给我的</p>
<p begin="5885040000t" end="5894620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">喂</p>
<p begin="5899640000t" end="5915910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">请问您现在一个人吗</p>
<p begin="5938010000t" end="5953440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">你先吃吧</p>
<p begin="5958450000t" end="5970130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">现在?</p>
<p begin="5970130000t" end="5986390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">我一个人在家</p>
<p begin="5995990000t" end="6007650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">好好吃</p>
<p begin="6011820000t" end="6032690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">最近还是都窝在家里</p>
<p begin="6032690000t" end="6046440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">这样啊</p>
<p begin="6052290000t" end="6086070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">我打算一边小酌一边看书到天亮</p>
<p begin="6086070000t" end="6096920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">社长</p>
<p begin="6096920000t" end="6115270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">我已经不是社长了</p>
<p begin="6115270000t" end="6128610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">失礼了</p>
<p begin="6134030000t" end="6146140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">室井先生</p>
<p begin="6146140000t" end="6157400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">怎么了</p>
<p begin="6157400000t" end="6201190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">我会等你开始新事业的</p>
<p begin="6222450000t" end="6238730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">那我要挂电话了</p>
<p begin="6238730000t" end="6253320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">之后的事就拜托你了</p>
<p begin="6253320000t" end="6273350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">好的  再见</p>
<p begin="6489380000t" end="6503160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">她就是这样</p>
<p begin="6503160000t" end="6544450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">确定犯案时间你没有不在场证明之后</p>
<p begin="6544450000t" end="6571970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">才下手杀人的吧</p>
<p begin="6571970000t" end="6603260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">但是饭冢为什么要陷害我</p>
<p begin="6603260000t" end="6625350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">我不记得做过什么会被她怨恨的事</p>
<p begin="6625350000t" end="6657480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">她跟美春应该也只见过几次而已</p>
<p begin="6662890000t" end="6694600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">她最近也有打过几次电话给我</p>
<p begin="6700860000t" end="6740050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">说警察去问话后得知美春被杀</p>
<p begin="6747980000t" end="6770920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">所以来问我有什么需要帮忙的吗</p>
<p begin="6770920000t" end="6816810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">还问之后能不能过来拜访…</p>
<p begin="6825140000t" end="6853930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">(室井先生)</p>
<p begin="6853930000t" end="6868510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">(请接电话)</p>
<p begin="6868510000t" end="6896880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">她竟然会想嫁祸给我</p>
<p begin="6896880000t" end="6912310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">到底为什么</p>
<p begin="6939420000t" end="6962360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">就算是我也无法得知动机的</p>
<p begin="6977380000t" end="7027840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">警方目前也正在追查是谁想陷害你</p>
<p begin="7027840000t" end="7048280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">就等她被逮捕之后再说吧</p>
<p begin="7067460000t" end="7132940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">她似乎没想过只有自己 知道你那天晚上的行踪</p>
<p begin="7138790000t" end="7167560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">大概是完全没想到你很满足于跟雪女交流</p>
<p begin="7167560000t" end="7219280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">真的过着彻底与一般社会隔离的生活吧</p>
<p begin="7226790000t" end="7245970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">所以才会这么大意</p>
<p begin="7245970000t" end="7268500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">说不定很快就会被逮捕了呢</p>
<p begin="7298120000t" end="7312720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">你要振作</p>
<p begin="7319800000t" end="7341070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">这并不是你的错</p>
<p begin="7372350000t" end="7385280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">我不会被打败的</p>
<p begin="7395290000t" end="7414070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">就算是我的错…</p>
<p begin="7429500000t" end="7454940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">你是为了让我能承受这个真相</p>
<p begin="7454940000t" end="7487480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">才先说出那些骗人的推理吧</p>
<p begin="7494140000t" end="7510410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">你认为如果我没先听过那些话</p>
<p begin="7510410000t" end="7547110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">说不定会变得更加无法相信一切</p>
<p begin="7552540000t" end="7574650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">毕竟我可是智慧之神啊</p>
<p begin="7574650000t" end="7594240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">当然是深思熟虑过咯</p>
<p begin="7594240000t" end="7605090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">可是</p>
<p begin="7605090000t" end="7637210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">你竟然连警方的搜查状况都能掌握</p>
<p begin="7637210000t" end="7661390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">这也是智慧之神的洞察力吗</p>
<p begin="7661390000t" end="7711870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">我只是请幽灵去警察局偷听而已</p>
<p begin="7711870000t" end="7755240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">所以才会很早就知道你的嫌疑减轻了</p>
<p begin="7760660000t" end="7781930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">用这种方法没问题吗</p>
<p begin="7781930000t" end="7803610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">这样快速又确实啊</p>
<p begin="7807380000t" end="7816970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">顺带一提</p>
<p begin="7816970000t" end="7851160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">犯案现场的河岸也有好几个幽灵</p>
<p begin="7851160000t" end="7872440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">它们都目击了犯案过程咯</p>
<p begin="7880370000t" end="7890380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">是女性</p>
<p begin="7890380000t" end="7912890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">身高大概155公分</p>
<p begin="7912890000t" end="7925410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">棕色头发</p>
<p begin="7925410000t" end="7975460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">从它们的证词得知真凶的特征和性别</p>
<p begin="7975460000t" end="8000900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">可以确定你真的不是犯人</p>
<p begin="8011330000t" end="8052610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">它们也目击了伪造死亡信息的场面</p>
<p begin="8052610000t" end="8078470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">所以我调查了与你有关的可能人物</p>
<p begin="8085150000t" end="8131870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">让目击犯罪过程的幽灵指认了饭冢渚</p>
<p begin="8138950000t" end="8181070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">所以你在推理前就知道犯人是谁了吗</p>
<p begin="8181070000t" end="8211100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">我一开始就说我知道真凶是谁啦</p>
<p begin="8216950000t" end="8241970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">接下来的事情我一概不会干涉</p>
<p begin="8248230000t" end="8281180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">无论是这个事件还是你跟雪女的关系</p>
