<p begin="8312880000t" end="8333310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">关系不可能长久</p>
<p begin="8342070000t" end="8370430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">即便如此仍是有蜜月期的</p>
<p begin="8380440000t" end="8398390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">就算时间短暂</p>
<p begin="8398390000t" end="8434240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">也会是段无可取代的时光吧</p>
