<p begin="8722450000t" end="8747890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">人跟妖怪的混血儿可是很辛苦的</p>
<p begin="8753310000t" end="8774180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">在小泉八云的故事中</p>
<p begin="8774180000t" end="8790860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">也有写到他们生了十个…</p>
<p begin="8790860000t" end="8807540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">果然还是要提这个吗</p>
