<p begin="9134120000t" end="9172060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">那个人不只吃了人鱼肉</p>
<p begin="9172060000t" end="9199600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">还吃了别的妖怪的肉</p>
<p begin="9199600000t" end="9231290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">是从而得到可怕力量的怪物啊</p>
