<p begin="9340150000t" end="9353500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">那个人是…</p>
<p begin="9416060000t" end="9453180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">跟那个比起来你真是太可爱了</p>
<p begin="9453180000t" end="9462780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">可爱…</p>
<p begin="9469460000t" end="9514080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">难怪我一直觉得有股腥臊的讨厌气息</p>
