<p begin="9627530000t" end="9647970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">难得你们气氛这么好</p>
<p begin="9647970000t" end="9682160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">快点回去床上好好干活吧</p>
<p begin="9682160000t" end="9693420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">没品</p>
<p begin="9693420000t" end="9701770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">喂</p>
<p begin="9725130000t" end="9749740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">那么公主殿下  九郎大人</p>
<p begin="9756400000t" end="9780180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">谢谢你们</p>
<p begin="9796020000t" end="9822300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">又是个很麻烦的事件呢</p>
<p begin="9828550000t" end="9859420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">只要指认犯人的话倒还简单的说</p>
<p begin="9865270000t" end="9886110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">看雪女那个样子</p>
<p begin="9886110000t" end="9912400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">请你躲起来果然是正确的</p>
<p begin="9928650000t" end="9968280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">这次的必要条件是让雪女挺身为室井说话</p>
<p begin="9982460000t" end="10012500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">妖怪本来就很难忤逆我</p>
<p begin="10012500000t" end="10028350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">要是连你也在场</p>
<p begin="10028350000t" end="10069220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">雪女肯定会怕得连声音都发不出来吧</p>
<p begin="10069220000t" end="10102990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">就算这样  你一开始也演得太过头了吧</p>
<p begin="10111760000t" end="10133450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">我看光是那样就够让她吓到闭嘴了</p>
<p begin="10138860000t" end="10167640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">因为一想象就火大起来了嘛</p>
<p begin="10167640000t" end="10194340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">这可要怪学长平常的态度哦</p>
<p begin="10201840000t" end="10211440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">说起来</p>
<p begin="10211440000t" end="10237300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">还不是因为你老是不写作业弄到来不及</p>
<p begin="10242710000t" end="10273580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">我才不得不跟来帮忙</p>
<p begin="10304870000t" end="10337810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">我帮你做好大纲跟收齐资料了</p>
<p begin="10337810000t" end="10352840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">给我乖乖写报告</p>
<p begin="10412480000t" end="10423740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">所以说</p>
<p begin="10423740000t" end="10458770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">那个叫饭冢渚的真凶  动机到底是什么</p>
<p begin="10458770000t" end="10478370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">你有查到对吧</p>
<p begin="10478370000t" end="10521750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">她很尊敬室井  而且深爱着他呢</p>
<p begin="10521750000t" end="10573880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">所以很气他的前妻背叛他搞外遇</p>
<p begin="10583070000t" end="10602670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">室井离开公司时</p>
<p begin="10602670000t" end="10619340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">她本来也想跟着走</p>
<p begin="10627690000t" end="10650640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">你肯留在公司的话</p>
<p begin="10650640000t" end="10670230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">我就能放心离开了</p>
<p begin="10670230000t" end="10706520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">室井看起来没有想再创业</p>
<p begin="10706520000t" end="10724450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">也不打算依赖她</p>
<p begin="10730710000t" end="10746550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">她判断这时主动接近</p>
<p begin="10746550000t" end="10768250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">也只会造成困扰  所以一直忍着</p>
<p begin="10768250000t" end="10810380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">但是室井因为难以相信他人一直没有行动</p>
<p begin="10810380000t" end="10825800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">就算过了好几个月</p>
<p begin="10825800000t" end="10848330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">还是窝在那个家中</p>
<p begin="10848330000t" end="10868350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">饭冢再也忍不下去</p>
<p begin="10868350000t" end="10898800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">为了改变现状才动了杀人的念头</p>
<p begin="10905060000t" end="10926730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">饭冢渚装作是在出差中</p>
<p begin="10926730000t" end="10957600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">偶然遇见美春并向她搭话</p>
<p begin="10965530000t" end="10977620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">这么说来</p>
<p begin="10977620000t" end="11021010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">室井先生问了我知不知道你的近况</p>
<p begin="11021010000t" end="11053940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">说不定是考虑要跟你复合呢</p>
<p begin="11072300000t" end="11095250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">她本打算以室井的话题为契机</p>
<p begin="11095250000t" end="11146130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">边闲聊边将美春引诱至没有人的地方</p>
<p begin="11146130000t" end="11185750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">但美春本来就担心遭到室井报复</p>
<p begin="11185750000t" end="11212860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">所以很在意前夫怎么会说这种话</p>
<p begin="11239550000t" end="11264150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">于是美春主动提议去河岸</p>
<p begin="11264150000t" end="11291690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">把事情讲得详细一点</p>
<p begin="11312120000t" end="11338820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">对饭冢渚来说正是不可多得的好机会</p>
<p begin="11424320000t" end="11459350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">然后美春就被杀害了</p>
<p begin="11482710000t" end="11538610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">为什么饭冢渚要伪造痕迹嫁祸给室井?</p>
<p begin="11538610000t" end="11565290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">如果她爱着或对他有执着的话</p>
<p begin="11565290000t" end="11594070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">就算要杀美春  也不会这样做吧</p>
<p begin="11594070000t" end="11615350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">最扭曲的就是这一点呢</p>
<p begin="11624930000t" end="11644960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">在离职后仍保持联络</p>
<p begin="11644960000t" end="11664550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">就算被当成杀人犯</p>
<p begin="11664550000t" end="11683330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">只要自己仍坚信他是无辜的</p>
<p begin="11683330000t" end="11703350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">保持着相同态度的话</p>
<p begin="11703350000t" end="11730870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">室井就有可能会依赖自己吧</p>
<p begin="11737550000t" end="11769240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">说不定哪天也会爱上自己</p>
<p begin="11776340000t" end="11821380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">当室井因杀人嫌疑感到痛苦孤单时</p>
<p begin="11821380000t" end="11863510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">只有她在一旁陪伴  相信并帮助他</p>
<p begin="11863510000t" end="11888110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">她就是想制造这样的情况</p>
<p begin="11918980000t" end="11958610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">所以只要是能让室井有一定程度的嫌疑</p>
<p begin="11958610000t" end="11992390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">而饭冢渚本人不会受到怀疑的对象</p>
<p begin="11992390000t" end="12014500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">其实不管杀谁她都无所谓</p>
<p begin="12014500000t" end="12035350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">真的很扭曲呢</p>
<p begin="12041610000t" end="12078730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">但要是室井真的被当犯人逮捕</p>
<p begin="12078730000t" end="12099160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">不就得不偿失了吗</p>
<p begin="12099160000t" end="12132950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">这点就是饭冢渚的误判了吧</p>
<p begin="12141280000t" end="12173400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">本来室井无法原谅过去的外遇这种事</p>
<p begin="12173400000t" end="12207190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">作为杀害前妻的动机来说很牵强</p>
<p begin="12211780000t" end="12249720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">死亡信息实际上作为证据的效力也很低</p>
<p begin="12249720000t" end="12276830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">那么就算室井被怀疑</p>
<p begin="12276830000t" end="12319390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">最后应该也会因嫌疑不足而不了了之吧</p>
<p begin="12332310000t" end="12364840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">结果这时突然冒出美春的告发信</p>
<p begin="12364840000t" end="12392780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">甚至出现了加深嫌疑的影像</p>
<p begin="12392780000t" end="12406140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">因为如此</p>
<p begin="12406140000t" end="12441590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">室井的嫌疑就越来越重</p>
<p begin="12441590000t" end="12469530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">变得有可能会被逮捕了</p>
<p begin="12469530000t" end="12482040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">原来如此</p>
<p begin="12487880000t" end="12532510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">所以犯人才没有在事件曝光过后的两周内</p>
<p begin="12532510000t" end="12575470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">继续伪造出更加不利于室井的证据吗</p>
<p begin="12581730000t" end="12621340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">我刚才有点犹豫要不要对室井说出这些</p>
<p begin="12629280000t" end="12666820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">但这动机对他来说太难接受了</p>
<p begin="12666820000t" end="12688080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">听了肯定会变得更加消沉</p>
<p begin="12697260000t" end="12743970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">警方要查明真相应该还需要些时间</p>
<p begin="12743970000t" end="12758560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">相信到时候</p>
<p begin="12758560000t" end="12790680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">室井也已经恢复到足以承受的状态了吧</p>
<p begin="12801530000t" end="12855750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">今晚是雪女和他建立深刻关系的大好机会</p>
<p begin="12855750000t" end="12889530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">要是告知会阻挠他们的事实</p>
<p begin="12889530000t" end="12909130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">我可是会被雪女怨恨的</p>
<p begin="12915800000t" end="12950010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">室井说不定天生自带烂桃花呢</p>
<p begin="12957510000t" end="12985050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">一开始差点被朋友杀的时候也是</p>
<p begin="12985050000t" end="13015900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">然后前妻杀人未遂也是</p>
<p begin="13020920000t" end="13036340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">加上这次的事件</p>
<p begin="13036340000t" end="13063050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">原因全都是出于女性关系呢</p>
<p begin="13072210000t" end="13108920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">他或许生来就容易被恶劣的女人缠上呢</p>
<p begin="13108920000t" end="13132690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">虽然这之中最恶劣的还是雪女了吧</p>
<p begin="13139360000t" end="13158550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">毕竟她还是妖怪</p>
<p begin="13158550000t" end="13190260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">尽管雪女深情貌美</p>
<p begin="13190260000t" end="13219870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">只要走错一步可是会被冻死的</p>
<p begin="13224030000t" end="13260320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">(民宅中发现被冷冻的怪异尸体!)<br />就算哪天看到室井被冻死的新闻</p>
<p begin="13260320000t" end="13275760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">我也不会感到意外呢</p>
<p begin="13296610000t" end="13304530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">不</p>
<p begin="13312030000t" end="13334570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">我也没办法这样笑人家呢</p>
<p begin="13360420000t" end="13374610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">你的前女友</p>
<p begin="13374610000t" end="13405470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">跟堂姐六花都是有些问题的人嘛</p>
<p begin="13410480000t" end="13437590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">不  最有问题的就是你了</p>
<p begin="13437590000t" end="13469280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">真失礼  你是在挑剔什么</p>
<p begin="13469280000t" end="13484710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">跟我说的一样</p>
<p begin="13484710000t" end="13506400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">公主殿下很厉害吧</p>
<p begin="13506400000t" end="13525580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">不过她的品行真的有问题</p>
<p begin="13525580000t" end="13533930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">喂</p>
<p begin="13541850000t" end="13585220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">我和她不可能这样一辈子</p>
<p begin="13585220000t" end="13606080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">我们的价值观和寿命都不同</p>
<p begin="13612760000t" end="13642780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">让别人看见我们走在一起也会引起问题吧</p>
<p begin="13653640000t" end="13665300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">即便如此</p>
<p begin="13665300000t" end="13696590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">我仍希望能再维持一阵子这样的时光</p>
<p begin="13737040000t" end="13748300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">怎么了</p>
<p begin="13754990000t" end="13767080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">没什么</p>
<p begin="13869680000t" end="13899710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">(待续)</p>
